title: Pics: It's just Khloe Kardashian doing lunges in a very small swimsuit - from all angles. NSFW(ish)
text:
Khloe Kardashian is the latest member of the family to have her own website and app, complete with monthly fee. But, depending on what you're in to (seemingly it's "all about that bass"), it could be money well spent. Here she is, just doing a work out while in St. Barths. She's got the correct footwear on courtesy of Nike, but sure who's looking at the footwear. Just me?
. @khloekardashian TO THE MAX pic.twitter.com/A5CKr3wGBp
— Complex Sneakers (@ComplexSneakers) October 7, 2015 See all the photos from @khloekardashian 's fitness photo shoot in St. Barths here: https://t.co/YwAOMuIpmy pic.twitter.com/M4kaUKb1mv
— Kardashian Pedia (@Kardashianpedia) October 7, 2015
. @khloekardashian really goes dumb pic.twitter.com/6Ic9pewNqh
— FREE BREAD (@FREEBREADINTL) October 8, 2015 Hang about, here's another angle.
Via khloewithak.com
